text: Very happy to worship at Orchard Presbyterian Church, easy to reach from MRT station & bus stop.  The welcome is warm & friendly, there are also worship fellowships where you can build friendships and get to know each other from various ethnicities. One of my experiences in the Martha & Maria worship service was that there was also a sailor's service, not only did we get to know each other, but we were also given the opportunity to share testimonies of our lives that we had experienced in God.
The church has services in Indonesian, English, Mandarin and German. For Indonesia, the service is at 2.30pm
